description._content: If reproduced or distributed, this image should be clearly attributed to the collection of the Australian National Maritime Museum; and not be used for any commercial or for-profit purposes without the permission of the museum. For more information see our Flickr Commons Rights Statement. The ANMM undertakes research and accepts public comments that enhance the information we hold about images in our collection. This record has been updated accordingly. This photograph is part of the Henry Stewart collection, which was originally part of the Australian War Memorial and was transferred to the ANMM. Object no.
